EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 1800Z DAILY
   25 FEB THRU 15 MAR WITHIN 23 MILES
   OF 57-35.2N 010-19.3W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD
   CONTACT HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL
   ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 151900Z MAR 13.
